<section>
  <h3>3. The Logger</h3>
  <p>To save information to log-files at runtime<br>
    Default file-name: <strong>Rails.root/log/environment_name.log</strong><br>
    Log levels: <strong>:debug</strong> (0)
                <strong>:info</strong> (1)
                <strong>:warn</strong> (2)
                <strong>:error</strong> (3)
                <strong>:fatal</strong> (4)
                <strong>:unknown</strong> (5)
                <br>
    Default log level: <%= ActiveRecord::Base.logger.level %>
  </p>
</section>

